             was indicted for <rs id="t17840526-124-off552" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840526-124-off552" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-124-off552" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17840526-124-cd553" type="crimeDate">3d of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840526-124-off552 t17840526-124-cd553"></join>, in the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17840526-124-victim1130" type="victimName">
                           Jerome 
                           Knapp
                        <interp inst="t17840526-124-victim1130" type="surname" value="Knapp"></interp>
